PART B — RS EXCEL CLASSIFIER: ACCEPT SINGLE-STRENGTH COMPOSITION
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Bug: RS classifier rejects the most common pharma composition format:
single-strength unit composition with one quantity column. Injection and
tablet Excels all fail with "This Excel has material names but no quantity,
strength, MDD, or amount-in-maximum-dose columns."

Examples currently failing:
- Trilaciclib injection Excel: S.No | Material code | Ingredient | Function
